videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham throws the perfect lob for Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk, who throws the hammer down.
videos.headline: Graham and Mykhailiuk connect for the alley-oop

videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham makes the pretty pass to Udoka Azubuike under the rim for the dunk as the Jayhawks lead by 11 at the half.
videos.headline: Graham continues to facilitate for the Jayhawks

videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham and Udoka Azubuike pick up where they left off in the first half, by connecting for the basket.
videos.headline: Graham and Azubuike execute the pick-and-roll to perfection

videos.description: Kansas' Lagerald Vick makes the bounce pass to get it to Udoka Azubuike, who puts in the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Azubuike continues to find success under the rim

videos.description: Baylor's Mark Vital throws down a two-handed dunk and draws the foul, as Baylor trails against Kansas.
videos.headline: Vital makes the and-1 dunk

videos.description: Baylor's Tyson Jolly stops Kansas' Marcus Garrett at the rim, who was set up by a fantastic Devonte' Graham overhead-bounce pass.
videos.headline: Jolly makes Kansas unhappy

videos.description: Baylor's King McClure drains a 3-pointer to give the Bears the lead over the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: McClure helps give Baylor the lead

videos.description: Kansas' Malik Newman finishes with the layup on the fastbreak to put the Jayhawks back on top against Baylor.
videos.headline: Newman helps give Kansas the lead

videos.description: Baylor fails to score on the inbounds play, and continues their struggles in Lawrence as they fall to Kansas 70-67.
videos.headline: Baylor turns it over as time expires

videos.description: Fran Fraschilla and Rich Hollenberg chat with Malik Newman as Newman speaks about the competitive nature of the Big 12 and looks ahead to facing Trae Young on January 23rd on ESPN.
videos.headline: Newman on Big 12 play: 'Every game is like a tournament game'
